            </mml:math>
          </disp-formula>
        </p>
        <p> which is equivalent to the more common formula <italic>Ï</italic><sup>2</sup>â=â<italic>E</italic>[<italic>N</italic><sup>2</sup>]âââ<italic>E</italic>[<italic>N</italic>]<sup>2</sup>. We have: </p>
        <p>
          <disp-formula>
